jKdd_fw">Thương xuân kỳ 3 - 傷春其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-ti%E1%BB%81n-ng%E1%BB%B1-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%A9-y%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BB%8Bch-trung-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-c%C3%BA/poem-5eNoK9QmCnasf1K-uaTysw">Tiết tiền ngự viên tứ yến, tịch trung đắc cú - 節前御園賜宴席中得句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81i-T%C3%A2n-Gi%C3%A1c-La-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/author-LWiJ3ebJ3gpU86_3bbLouw">Ái Tân Giác La Hoằng Lịch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-t%C3%B2ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-%C3%81-ph%C3%B3-H%C3%A0-T%C3%A2y-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-pJIF07o2Qkh5pVVW0kebdg">Tống tòng đệ Á phó Hà Tây phán quan - 送從弟亞赴河西判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-ph%C3%A1n-quan-ph%C3%B9-th%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0n-Ki%E1%BB%81m-Trung-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-khai-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-8YXOeoyNJfJKeuGwOcXFtQ">Tống Vương thập ngũ phán quan phù thị hoàn Kiềm Trung, đắc khai tự - 送王十五判官扶侍還黔中，得開字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Tung/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-O0QMdXGuqU7N-RdUk0b62w">Trúc chi ca kỳ 5 - 竹枝歌其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4n-Tung/author-8q1Pl4yTEAzPiO_vSuznIA">Tôn Tung</a>)<br></div>	</div>
